{"tid":1436490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家 合埋眼回想返過去兩個月所經歷既","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T10:23:29.000Z","uid":97523,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e08fd1de3ff619620ab9f75b734abcd3f3176014","tid":1436490,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"69<br />\n612<br />\n616<br />\n621<br />\n71<br />\n714<br />\n721<br />\n85<br />\n<br />\n對唔住各位<br />\n我只係記得以上日子既夢<br />\n其實啲畫面開始好模糊<br />\n已經唔記得邊日打邊日<br />\n食既每一粒辣蟹係幾時邊日<br />\n<br />\n見到依家政府開始打民生牌<br />\n想將焦點轉移落去狗記招<br />\n一直想分割呢場運動唔同人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">求下大家<br />\n無論做咩都好<br />\n團結一致 槍口對外 對準政權 清算警犬</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n發夢既事忘記咗都好<br />\n五大訴求 係一路都冇變<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家 睇到呢到<br />\n啱啱出現過既五大訴求係咪直接skip咗冇睇就拉落黎？<br />\n呢兩個月呢五大訴求睇得太多次 <br />\n我懇請各位香港人 拉返上去 認真地睇多次<br />\n問下自己呢場運動既目標係乜<br />\n唔好比任何人轉移到視線！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9ded972ef4e5ce5cebf4a9c5a1cfea3ffbab864d","tid":1436490,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a523ec42934de4f5d566df093cd89d804ff1e1bf","tid":1436490,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a323456eec33f656a18947e94b9d5a36d1c07b","tid":1436490,"uid":285774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42cbd2777701d9601a3d3dfde32fd9a44e11750","tid":1436490,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:00:44.000Z","msg":"求下大家"},{"pid":"e20a9448121d508e454615996695a02c8f72a3f9","tid":1436490,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:03:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed0efa9f759d9148b4d711b7c726c7dfb122e0bc","tid":1436490,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:23:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}